title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 13)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

It will be nice to get back to normal around here.  And all the people said Amen!  :-)

INDIE: Aaron Hale.  HIP-HOP/RAP: Alchemist And Budgie, Alex Faith, Cheno Lyfe, Christon Gray, DC Comets, DJ Wade-O, Donovan Charles, Izreal Graham, Levi Hinson, Milan Credle.  GOSPEL: Bobbie Jones.  POP: Chayah Mirand, Hillary McBride, Kari Jobe.  ALTERNATIVE: Copeland, Emery, Manchester Orchestra, Randy Gordon.  JAZZ: James Brandon Lewis.  CLASSICAL: John Tavener.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Seed.  FOLK: Seeds Of Saints.  INSTRUMENTAL: Zamar Sound.
